```plantuml
@startuml LouisvilleMetro_WazeCCPProcessor
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor "Waze CCP Feed" as WazeFeed
actor "API Consumer" as APIConsumer

package "AWS Cloud" {
  rectangle "S3 Bucket\n(Data Lake)" as S3Bucket #lightblue
  rectangle "SQS Queue" as SQS #lightblue
  rectangle "SNS Topic" as SNS #lightblue
  rectangle "API Gateway" as APIGateway #lightblue
  database "Aurora PostgreSQL" as AuroraDB #lightblue

  rectangle "Lambda Functions" {
    rectangle "waze-data-download" as DownloadLambda #lightgreen
    rectangle "waze-data-process" as ProcessLambda #lightgreen
    rectangle "waze-data-alerts-processing" as AlertsLambda #lightgreen
    rectangle "waze-data-jams-processing" as JamsLambda #lightgreen
    rectangle "waze-data-irregularities-processing" as IrregularitiesLambda #lightgreen
    rectangle "waze-db-initialize" as DBInitializeLambda #lightgreen
    rectangle "waze-data-api" as APILambda #lightgreen
  }
}

WazeFeed --> DownloadLambda : Fetch Data
DownloadLambda --> S3Bucket : Store JSON Files
S3Bucket --> ProcessLambda : Trigger on New File

ProcessLambda --> SQS : Queue Data Processing
SQS --> AlertsLambda : Process Alerts
SQS --> JamsLambda : Process Jams
SQS --> IrregularitiesLambda : Process Irregularities

AlertsLambda --> AuroraDB : Store Alerts
JamsLambda --> AuroraDB : Store Jams
IrregularitiesLambda --> AuroraDB : Store Irregularities

DBInitializeLambda --> AuroraDB : Init & Update Schema

APIConsumer --> APIGateway : API Requests
APIGateway --> APILambda : Route Requests
APILambda --> AuroraDB : Query Data

ProcessLambda --> SNS : Notify Processing Status
@enduml
```